src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f954e755c08fbe1d2d672a0242f295ca3ab1c06e","tid":331604,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kamwai.sin/posts/10154793544802467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkamwai.sin%2Fposts%2F10154793544802467&d=HMuP90IvOVsN92u50nRxLV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=cd0e8604\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kamwai.sin/posts/10154793544802467</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk01.life/videos/10159092044080215/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk01.life%2Fvideos%2F10159092044080215%2F&d=HMuP90IvOVsN92u50nRxLV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=304f80c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk01.life/videos/10159092044080215/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完呢D機械人嘅AI<br />\n我會覺得十年後好多服務性行業員工都會失業</blockquote><br />\n麥當勞都用機叫嘢食<br />\n<br />\n元氣壽司都用玩具火車送嘢食<br />\n<br />\n侍應等着失業</blockquote><br />\n好寒<br />\n「你希望毀滅世界嗎？」<br />\n「是的」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/053351_9fdb58252acbd61e9def3b88ae4ad4f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F053351_9fdb58252acbd61e9def3b88ae4ad4f1.jpg&h=f274d1fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n條片last 一個鏡頭真係搞到我好不安"},{"pid":"3f62d98b08c7ed7f67e47e8b95cb522ca44e1ff3","tid":331604,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係物聯網<br />\n3d打印難小小<br />\n始終家用3d打印機可以做到的實用物品唔多<br />\n材料又未必識整<br />\n最多都只係當玩具玩</blockquote><br />\n其實3d printing已經好多年<br />\n仲未做到真正普及</blockquote><br />\n有用的野先會普及到<br />\n始終普通人日常生活唔會用到3d打印技術<br />\n製造業同醫療行業大機會d用到3d printing<br />\n有冇可能用3d printing起樓呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b18372906d30fa50ff624cc8f61fe805c2f10